title: www.nwosurvival.com
description:
This is a small collection of pdf&#039;s (many public domain) taken from
a website that is likely to be shut down soon.  The original site for
these pdf&#039;s is http://www.librum.us/ .  It seems that the original site
isn&#039;t using the pdf format anymore, instead trying to use restrictive
windows applications to contain the books.

Many of these books are old cook books, and old gardening books
and it may be pleasant to read these from time to time.  I will try to
maintain the seed as long as I possibly can, but I can&#039;t make any
guarantees that the seed will be anywhere close to permanent.  If
the site, http://www.nwosurvival.com/ , is still up and running, you
may want to get the pdf&#039;s from there, and help seed this torrent.
The bandwidth at that site is much larger than mine.  I&#039;m posting
these here, since that site may disappear in the near future.

Thanks :)
